<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Il <strong>condizionale</strong> e il <strong>congiuntivo</strong> sono spesso usati nella stessa frase quando si vuole esprimere un'ipotesi o una possibilità. In questo caso il congiuntivo è quasi sempre preceduto da <em>se</em>. Osserva.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border-2 border-amber-200">
        <p class="font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2">CONDIZIONALE PRESENTE → CONGIUNTIVO IMPERFETTO</p>
        <p><span class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Andrei</span> al mare → se <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">fosse</span> bel tempo.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border-2 border-amber-200">
        <p class="font-bold text-orange-600 mb-2">CONDIZIONALE PASSATO → CONGIUNTIVO TRAPASSATO</p>
        <p><span class="text-orange-600 font-semibold">Sarei andato</span> al mare → se <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">fosse stato</span> bel tempo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      <span>Sottolinea <span class="text-orange-600">condizionale<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-orange-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="orange" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span> e <span class="text-blue-600">congiuntivo<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span>.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">Andrei</span> a giocare in giardino se <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">facesse</span> meno freddo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">Vorrei</span> che tu <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">prestassi</span> più attenzione alle mie spiegazioni.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Se <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">avessimo conosciuto</span> prima la verità, <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">avremmo dato</span> un giudizio diverso.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="orange">Saremmo</span> molto contenti se tu <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">venissi</span> a trovarci.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Highlight correct form -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Colora la forma verbale corretta.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Se tu
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_1" value="avessi" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avessi</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_1" value="avresti" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avresti</span></label>
          davvero voglia,
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_2" value="camminerai" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">camminerai</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_2" value="cammineresti" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">cammineresti</span></label>
          ancora.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Se
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_3" value="cambieresti" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">cambieresti</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_3" value="cambiassi" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">cambiassi</span></label>
          idea sull'argomento, fammelo sapere.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">•
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_4" value="Sarei partito" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">Sarei partito</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_4" value="Fossi partito" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">Fossi partito</span></label>
          se non mi
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_5" value="avessero" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avessero</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_5" value="avrebbero" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avrebbero</span></label>
          trattenuto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Ti
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_6" value="avrei telefonato" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avrei telefonato</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_6" value="telefonassi" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">telefonassi</span></label>
          se
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_7" value="avessi saputo" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avessi saputo</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_7" value="sapessi" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">sapessi</span></label>
          che stai male.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Se
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_8" value="leggerebbe" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">leggerebbe</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_8" value="leggesse" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">leggesse</span></label>
          il giornale,
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_9" value="saprebbe" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">saprebbe</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex2_9" value="sapesse" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">sapesse</span></label>
          come sono andate le cose.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Esercizi pp. <%= link_to "166", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p166"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %>, <%= link_to "167", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p167"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %> e <%= link_to "169", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p169"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %></p>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
